## **Overview**
## **Key Functionalities**



> 1. **Ingest mailbox**
> 2. **Make Neo4j Graph Database**
> 3. **Auto Indexing**
> 4. **Topic modeling and Sentiment Extraction**
> 5. **Pre-defined Query Support**

